{"tid":1644188,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插沙跪求和理非戴罩] 全民口罩既八個理由","createTime":"2019-10-10T12:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T16:26:48.000Z","uid":190579,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eff61b41e7baff57c87baa53955b159bdc6386c2","tid":1644188,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:51:39.000Z","msg":"睇重點就跳去第5條<br />\n左膠請由第1條睇起易入口D，睇哂佢<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>1. 無成本抗爭</ins></span></span></ins><br />\n平日戴口罩<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔犯法</span></strong>，警犬叫到就除<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>2. 抗爭日常化</ins></span></span><br />\n大型集中遊行太傷，每次都起碼幾十勇武被捕。抗爭要日常化先可以延續。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>3. 公民抗命</ins></span></span></ins><br />\n用不合作運動表達對惡法的不滿。增加警犬執法成本。當全街都係口罩，警犬根本不可能執法，叫人除罩。變相係靠<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>民間力量廢除惡法</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>4. 保護私隱</ins></span></span></ins><br />\n而家周街都係高清人面辨識cam，因為政府已經舖路搞緊社會信用計劃，甚至係集中營。戴個口罩防止自己私隱被政府收集。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>5. 製造環境比正義降臨</ins></span></span><br />\n你哋和理非睇天降單車，鶳，裝修唔係睇得好心涼既嗎？<br />\n唔想整污糟自己隻手，但又祈求有勇武降臨，做你想做又唔敢做既事，然後代你坐監。<br />\n成日問問問幾時先有麻包袋。用你做閪腦諗下，全街冇人口罩，冇人黑衫，叫勇武點樣麻包袋後全身而退？<br />\n全民口罩係基本消費，最好著埋黑衫。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>6. 反向白色恐怖</ins></span></span></ins><br />\n諗下一隻休班狗落街見到咁多口罩有咩感覺。<br />\n警犬已經唔驚起底，但全民口罩加起底既協同效應就可以令警犬嚇到瀨尿。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>7. 防止後生仔女被擄走</ins></span></span><br />\n而家警犬藍屍已經去到周街捉落單後生仔女番去<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">強姦謀殺</span></strong>既地步，而我哋係防不勝防。但全民口罩就可以令佢哋難D落手。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>8. 製造救人條件</ins></span></span><br />\n和理人你要明白，嗌放人係冇撚用的。而我都明白，和理非唔敢救人既顧慮，你驚瀨野上身呀嘛。我都明白，人之常情。但有口罩就唔同講法，就算你唔救人，你都可以透過增加警犬認人難度，去救救人既人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我求你和理非戴口罩啦<br />\n前線做咁多嘢<br />\n但你連口罩都唔敢戴<br />\n根本就係坐緊順風車<br />\n你哋再係咁，我唔玩咖啦</span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>FAQ:</strong></span></span><br />\nQ: 犯法喎<br />\nA: 平時戴口罩唔犯法，警犬叫到唔除先犯法<br />\n<br />\nQ: 怕喺公司比藍C督灰<br />\nA: 搭車戴，到office除。或者收工戴。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 怕比警犬拉<br />\nA: 人多就係力量，好似我哋冇不反書都照遊行到咁。"},{"pid":"7143cda9bdf6e4d296bf47daa5a811f64a2c47bc","tid":1644188,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"遠水 希望有4000和理非幫手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1638741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1638741</a>"},{"pid":"026b1f80ccfd50a7d9abce1eb2b4c374ed27b221","tid":1644188,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b817c83dec6908cfff60c3a5870086e51c7ae3ab","tid":1644188,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59ed54936d0c98cc6a9bdc456b7febf1175b295","tid":1644188,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8955196b8e41824f0868fb47fd6bb74274fdc51e","tid":1644188,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:03:04.000Z","msg":"冇人理？"},{"pid":"fea3b68e91b77db646599fa5a526c769cbd85c3d","tid":1644188,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:04:04.000Z","msg":"推，今日行左五分鐘街，一個口罩都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a335078c7b3decace3ad48a3209db2da0ad4e14f","tid":1644188,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fea3b68e91b77db646599fa5a526c769cbd85c3d","tid":1644188,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:04:04.000Z","msg":"推，今日行左五分鐘街，一個口罩都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edb460bebb181b443448b9f5f514a8e2bd42dc8","tid":1644188,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:22:01.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79c60e7f355b741a76176f7faf24a2dc4b254bc7","tid":1644188,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"push"}]}